  ('D6101', 'Debridement of a peri-implant defect or defects surrounding a single implant, and surface', 'VIII. IMPLANT SERVICES D6000-D6199', (select id from src), 45, 'D6101 Debridement of a peri-implant defect or defects surrounding a single implant, and surface cleaning of the exposed implant surfaces, including flap entry and closure (TOOTH) (PA REQUIRED) (POST OPERATIVE CARE: 30 DAYS) $252.50'),
