  ('D7414', ', and D7415 must be submitted with a copy of the pathology and operative report(s). All operative reports must', 'X. ORAL AND MAXILLOFACIAL SURGERY D7000-D7999', (select id from src), 51, 'D7414, and D7415 must be submitted with a copy of the pathology and operative report(s). All operative reports must include a description of the lesion and its location. D7414 Excision of malignant lesion greater than 1.25cm (REPORT NEEDED) (POST OPERATIVE CARE: 60 DAYS) (BR)'),
  ('D7415', 'Excision of malignant lesion complicated (REPORT NEEDED) (POST OPERATIVE CARE: 60 DAYS) (BR)', 'X. ORAL AND MAXILLOFACIAL SURGERY D7000-D7999', (select id from src), 52, 'D7415 Excision of malignant lesion complicated (REPORT NEEDED) (POST OPERATIVE CARE: 60 DAYS) (BR) Excision of Intra-Osseous Lesions Claims must be submitted with a copy of the pathology and operative report(s) and must include a description of the lesion and its location. Reimbursement for routine or surgical extractions includes removal of tooth, soft tissue associated with the root and curettage of the socket. Periapical granulomas at the apex of decayed teeth will not be separately reimbursed in addition to the tooth extraction.'),
